creator: d17o
descriptionHtml:
Air Crew Now allows airline cabin crew members to check their flight schedule at a glance.

It is possible to try the application for free and, if you are satisfied, use it under a monthly subscription that you can unsubscribe whenever you want.

Currently only available for Vueling, but we will be adding more airlines in future updates.

Air Crew Now depends on the availability of flight plan information from the airlines in the aims ecrew system, and therefore there may be interruptions in the service if such data becomes unavailable for reasons beyond our control.
